{"data":[{"date":"15:59 05/07","title":"\u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e2y k\u00edn t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n bay d\u00f9 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/dt-nhat-ban-duoc-chao-don-nhu-nhung-nguoi-hung-du-bi-loai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u00e0ng tr\u0103m ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp trung t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n bay Narita (Chiba) \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng d\u00f9 ph\u1ea3i v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc sau v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.</h2><div>\r\n<h2>H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n bay khi v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc:</h2>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/5/Wild-scenes-at-Narita-Airport-as-Samurai-Blue-returns-home\uff1aThe-Asahi-Shimbun.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><br>\r\n<img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n</h2>\r\n<div>Sau khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018, \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ed1ng m\u00e1y bay v\u00e0o s\u00e1ng 5/7 (theo gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng). D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 vi\u1ebft n\u00ean c\u1ed9t m\u1ed1c m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng khi c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng 800 c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n bay Narita (Chiba) \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng d\u00f9 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng d\u00f9 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/dt-nhat-ban-duoc-chao-don-nhu-nhung-nguoi-hung-du-bi-loai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n khi xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n bay sau khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \"samurai xanh\", qu\u00e2y k\u00edn l\u1ed1i \u0111i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n khi xu\u1ed1ng s\u1ea3nh s\u00e2n bay. Th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Akira Nishino \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng v\u00e2y c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c l\u00e0 NHM Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng chen l\u1ea5n, x\u00f4 \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi g\u1ea7n th\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>M\u1ed9t ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Setagaya Ward (Tokyo) \u0111\u00e3 t\u1edbi s\u00e2n bay t\u1eeb \u0111\u00eam h\u00f4m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n cho bi\u1ebft: \"T\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng khi Keisuke Honda ghi b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Senegal. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\"T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n h\u00e9t l\u1edbn l\u00ean 'c\u1ea3m \u01a1n' v\u00e0 'c\u00e1c anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t'.\"<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u1ea9ng cao \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div>\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 ba \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup, hai l\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0o c\u00e1c n\u0103m 2002 v\u00e0 2010. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, \"samurai xanh\" \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T B\u1ec9 hai b\u00e0n \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua trong nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>Sau khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac, hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e0 Keisuke Honda (32 tu\u1ed5i) v\u00e0 Makoto Hasebe (34 tu\u1ed5i) \u0111\u1ec1u tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 chia tay \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-bi-32-nhat-ban-421-190297.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 3-2 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hazard-tiet-lo-su-khac-biet-cua-dt-bi-421-190265.html\">Hazard ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/don-quyet-dinh-tieu-diet-samurai-xanh-cua-bi-su-dong-gop-tinh-te-cua-lukaku-421-190257.html\">\u0110\u00f2n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u00eau di\u1ec7t Samurai xanh c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9: S\u1ef1 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p tinh t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Lukaku</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/nhat-ban-roi-world-cup-2018-tieng-vong-tu-chau-a-466-190253.html\">Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n chia tay World Cup 2018: Ti\u1ebfng v\u1ecdng t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u \u00c1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/nhung-hinh-anh-an-tuong-trong-ngay-nhat-ban-thua-bi-465-190248.html\">Nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong ng\u00e0y Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n su\u00fdt l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/suyt-lam-nen-dia-chan-truoc-bi-nhat-ban-lap-ky-luc-world-cup-465-190240.html\">Su\u00fdt l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c World Cup</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"930","checkdouble":"190430"},{"date":"16:18 05/07","title":"Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/tiet-lo-ronaldo-da-ky-hop-dong-voi-juventus.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb c\u1ef1u gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia, Luciano Moggi. Theo \u0111\u00f3, qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1ea3o gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 CR7 \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf xong xu\u00f4i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd t\u1edbi Juventus</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A, Juventus \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro d\u00e0nh cho Cristiano Ronaldo. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 33, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u1eabn ghi t\u1edbi 44 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Real Madrid \u1edf m\u00f9a 2017/18, c\u00f9ng h\u1ecd l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n, trong 9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Ronaldo lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Madrid. V\u1edbi tham v\u1ecdng chinh ph\u1ee5c c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Champions League \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, Juventus r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a CR7. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/nguoi-juventus-som-mo-ve-song-sat-tai-hop-ronaldo-higuain-184-190405.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juve s\u1edbm m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 song s\u00e1t t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Ronaldo - Higuain</span> t\u1ea1i CLB.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Moggi ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Moggi ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/Moggi-tiet-lo-Ronaldo-da-ky-hop-dong-voi-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Juventus chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Ronaldo</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLuciano Moggi t\u1eebng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Juventus t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1994 \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2006. Trong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, d\u1ef1a theo ngu\u1ed3n tin m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, \u00f4ng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cRonaldo \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua cu\u1ed9c ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf v\u1edbi Juventus t\u1ea1i Munich\u201d, Moggi n\u00f3i tr\u00ean k\u00eanh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh Italia, Tele7Gold. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 trong \u0111\u1ea7u sau khi n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt quan tr\u1ecdng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u1eebng \u201cv\u1ed3 h\u1ee5t\u201d Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Moggi t\u1eebng mu\u1ed1n Ronaldo tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Juventus n\u0103m 2002. Khi \u0111\u00f3, Ronaldo v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Sporting Lisbon song \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tri\u1ec3n v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo chuan bi chuyen toi Juventus\" title=\"Ronaldo chuan bi chuyen toi Juventus\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/tiet-lo-ronaldo-da-ky-hop-dong-voi-juventus.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Moggi ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMoggi t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb mua Ronaldo v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 Marcelo Salas di chuy\u1ec3n theo h\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i song b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh. Sau \u0111\u00f3, CR7 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Manchester United v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2003. \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean\u201d, c\u1ef1u gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Juve n\u00f3i. \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1edbi quan s\u00e1t c\u1eadu \u1ea5y thi \u0111\u1ea5u khi m\u1edbi 18 tu\u1ed5i song \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 ch\u1eefng ch\u1ea1c.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ronaldo v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f4ng may, Marcelo Salas \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Sporting Lisbon v\u00ec mu\u1ed1n quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i River Plate. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1ea3 th\u00eam 5 tri\u1ec7u Euro cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 18 tu\u1ed5i, nh\u01b0ng n\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-va-messi-dat-tay-nhau-ve-nuoc-doan-ket-cuoc-hanh-trinh-421-190180.html\">Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi d\u1eaft tay nhau v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc: \u0110o\u1ea1n k\u1ebft cu\u1ed9c h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-la-messi-la-ronaldo-cua-dt-anh-421-190088.html\">Harry Kane l\u00e0 Messi, l\u00e0 Ronaldo c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/cristiano-ronaldo-ra-quyet-dinh-ve-tuong-lai-sau-tran-thua-cua-dt-bo-dao-nha-465-190053.html\">Cristiano Ronaldo ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thua-uruguay-hlv-bo-dao-nha-xin-ronaldo-mot-dieu-421-190047.html\">Thua Uruguay, HLV B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha xin Ronaldo m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"929","checkdouble":"190431"},{"date":"16:31 05/07","title":"C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/cap-nhat-tinh-hinh-luc-luong-cua-dt-anh-truoc-tran-gap-thuy-dien.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng 1/8. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i tiki-taka l\u1ed7i th\u1eddi l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn cho La Roja kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n xa. Nh\u01b0ng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n \u201cB\u00f2 t\u00f3t\u201d b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1edbm c\u0169ng l\u00e0 v\u00ec 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.</h2><h2>Koke</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i c\u1ea1nh Sergio Busquets \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 La Roja. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 8 thi \u0111\u1ea5u thi\u1ebfu hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng nh\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ed1t cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/3-cau-thu-gay-that-vong-nhat-cua-DT-Tay-Ban-Nha-o-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Koke ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKoke \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8. C\u0169ng nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, Koke ch\u1ec9 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u1edf kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1ee9 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a anh thi\u1ebfu h\u1eb3n \u0111i t\u00ednh s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Koke v\u00e0o trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m c\u1ee7a Nga c\u0169ng thi\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1ecb trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1. T\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n, c\u00fa s\u00fat penalty c\u1ee7a Koke kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 b\u1ecb Akinfeev \u0111\u1ea9y ra kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 Koke \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i d\u01b0\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>David Silva\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Silva\" title=\"David Silva\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/162516-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>David Silva tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Silva l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Man City c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha trong m\u1ed9t n\u0103m qua. Anh l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0a Man City l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh Premier League \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a La Roja trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, David Silva \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018. Anh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t m\u1ecdi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o. Silva v\u1eabn ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 Iran nh\u01b0ng anh ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t h\u01a1n qua t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nga, David Silva l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i k\u00e9m nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng &ldquo;B\u00f2 t\u00f3t&rdquo;. Anh b\u1ecb c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Nga l\u1ea5y b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. D\u1eabu cho v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng David Silva kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00e0o l\u00ean tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n n\u00e0o cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 b\u1ecb thay ra s\u1edbm b\u1edfi l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Iniesta trong hi\u1ec7p hai.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>David De Gea\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Gea\" title=\"De Gea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/162625-3.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>De Gea kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n v\u1eefng ch\u00e3i \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">De Gea l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean h\u01a1n c\u1ea3. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1edfi tranh, De Gea \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 l\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAnh kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u World Cup b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n. C\u00fa s\u00fat \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo b\u1ed7ng nhi\u00ean tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng khi De Gea b\u1eaft h\u1ee5t b\u00f3ng y h\u1ec7t nh\u1eefng ch\u00e0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nghi\u1ec7p d\u01b0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nX\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1edf World Cup, De Gea c\u0169ng n\u1eb1m trong nh\u00f3m nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh k\u00e9m nh\u1ea5t. Trong s\u1ed1 7 c\u00fa s\u00fat ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t, De Gea ch\u1ec9 c\u1ee9u thua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 6 b\u00e0n thua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDe Gea c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u1ea3 penalty n\u00e0o \u1edf lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang v\u1edbi Nga. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 De Gea kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1edbm \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t De Gea xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u01a1n c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd gi\u00fap La Roja ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u h\u01a1n th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0110T&nbsp;T\u00e2y Ban Nha:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-bi-co-the-dan-dat-tay-ban-nha-sau-world-cup-2018-421-190427.html\">HLV B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft T\u00e2y Ban Nha sau World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ky-world-cup-cua-tay-ban-nha-khong-te-nhu-nguoi-ta-nghi-421-190397.html\">K\u1ef3 World Cup c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta ngh\u0129</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"928","checkdouble":"190432"},{"date":"17:02 05/07","title":"Arsenal nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c bu\u1ed3n v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Argentina","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/arsenal-nhan-tin-cuc-buon-vu-sao-khung-argentina.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Ever Banega th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi Sevilla thay v\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Emirates.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal quan t\u00e2m Ever Banega\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Unai Emery \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nh\u1eb1m thay th\u1ebf s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Jack Wilshere, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. Mirror v\u00e0 ESPN kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 quan t\u00e2m Ever Banega c\u1ee7a Sevilla.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Ever Banega \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Ever Banega \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Kha-nang-Arsenal-mua-Ever-Banega-dang-rat-kho-khan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal chi 20 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Banega</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Sevilla v\u00e0o n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i v\u00e0 nhanh ch\u00f3ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1edbi 51 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBanega l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. M\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i anh ghi 7 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 5 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Emery \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao s\u1ef1 \u0111a n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n Arsenal chi 20 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Sevilla c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Banega t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i r\u1eddi Sevilla</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Ever Banega th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi Sevilla thay v\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Emirates.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal muon mua Banega\" title=\"Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua Banega\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/Arsenal-muon-mua-Ever-Banega-cua-Sevilla-voi-gia-25-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Banega tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Sevilla</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha, anh mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Banega cam k\u1ebft g\u1eafn b\u00f3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi Sevilla nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c. Lucas Torreira c\u1ee7a Sampdoria c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Banega, Arsenal c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Steven N'Zonzi, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Sevilla. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"927","checkdouble":"190433"},{"date":"17:09 05/07","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, Tam S\u01b0 \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/truoc-vong-tu-ket-tam-su-don-nhan-vien-binh-chat-luong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Gareth Southgate \u0111ang \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin l\u1ea1c quan, khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111a n\u0103ng Fabian Delph tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.\r\n</h2><h2>Delph \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man City \u0111\u00e3 xin ph\u00e9p HLV Gareth Southgate v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 &ldquo;h\u1ed9 \u0111\u00ea&rdquo;. Theo \u0111\u00f3, v\u1ee3 anh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb sinh \u0111\u1ee9a con th\u1ee9 3, v\u00e0 Fabian Delph \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc chuy\u00ean c\u01a1, gi\u00fap anh ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m th\u1eddi gian t\u1ed1i \u0111a.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3n ti\u1ec3u c\u00f4ng ch\u00faa ch\u00e0o \u0111\u1eddi trong s\u1ef1 m\u1eebng r\u1ee1. Anh cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua 24 gi\u1edd tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh em v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng 1/8 trong tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1eeb tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ec3 x\u00e1c. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 m\u1ecdi qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng trong nh\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i, nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;V\u00e0o l\u00fac 7:52 s\u00e1ng, t\u00f4i v\u00e0 v\u1ee3 c\u00f9ng 2 c\u00f4 con g\u00e1i xinh \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n m\u1ed9t thi\u00ean th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 di\u1ec5n t\u1ea3 n\u1ed5i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u&rdquo; &ndash; Fabian Delph chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean Instagram.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Delph tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh sau khi \u0111\u00f3n con g\u00e1i th\u1ee9 3\" title=\"Delph tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh sau khi \u0111\u00f3n con g\u00e1i th\u1ee9 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/delph.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Delph tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh sau khi \u0111\u00f3n con g\u00e1i th\u1ee9 3</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Delph \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Pep Guardiola s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed wingback c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u1ea1 l\u1eabm d\u00f9 s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd cho HLV Gareth Southgate th\u00eam nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n nay, Tam S\u01b0 v\u1eabn \u0111ang s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Ashley Young \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i, v\u00e0 Danny Rose l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng, nh\u01b0 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Colombia v\u1eeba qua. C\u00f2n v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Fabian Delph tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0110T Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m nh\u01b0 s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa s\u01b0 t\u1eed s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n &ndash; m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi ti\u1ec1m \u1ea9n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t s\u1eafc s\u1ea3o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tu-ket-world-cup-2018-hay-de-y-nguoi-anh-421-190417.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/tu-ket-world-cup-2018-hay-de-y-nguoi-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tu-ket-world-cup-2018-hay-de-y-nguoi-anh-421-190417.html\">T\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: H\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh</span><br>\r\nT\u1eeb m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1eb3ng ai quan t\u00e2m, \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u, sau khi \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-colombia-461-190305.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/Ket-qua-Colombia-vs-Anh-tran-dau-vong-18-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh-3.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-colombia-461-190305.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Colombia 1-1 (pen 3-4) Anh (V\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nT\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 bi k\u1ecbch \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Tam S\u01b0 khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd v\u00e0 \u1edf lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Henderson l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean s\u00fat h\u1ecfng (c\u1ea7n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"926","checkdouble":"190434"},{"date":"16:28 05/07","title":"World Cup 2018: 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/world-cup-2018-3-cau-thu-gay-that-vong-nhat-cua-dt-tay-ban-nha.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng 1/8. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i tiki-taka l\u1ed7i th\u1eddi l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn cho La Roja kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n xa. Nh\u01b0ng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n \u201cB\u00f2 t\u00f3t\u201d b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1edbm c\u0169ng l\u00e0 v\u00ec 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng.</h2><h2>Koke</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i c\u1ea1nh Sergio Busquets \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 La Roja. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 8 thi \u0111\u1ea5u thi\u1ebfu hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 trong ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng nh\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ed1t cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/3-cau-thu-gay-that-vong-nhat-cua-DT-Tay-Ban-Nha-o-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Koke ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKoke \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8. C\u0169ng nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, Koke ch\u1ec9 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u1edf kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1ee9 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a anh thi\u1ebfu h\u1eb3n \u0111i t\u00ednh s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Koke v\u00e0o trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m c\u1ee7a Nga c\u0169ng thi\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1ecb trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1. T\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n, c\u00fa s\u00fat penalty c\u1ee7a Koke kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 b\u1ecb Akinfeev \u0111\u1ea9y ra kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 Koke \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i d\u01b0\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>David Silva\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Silva\" title=\"David Silva\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/162516-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>David Silva tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Silva l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t \u1edf Man City c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha trong m\u1ed9t n\u0103m qua. Anh l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u01b0a Man City l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh Premier League \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a La Roja trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, David Silva \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018. Anh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t m\u1ecdi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o. Silva v\u1eabn ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00e0 Iran nh\u01b0ng anh ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t h\u01a1n qua t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nga, David Silva l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i k\u00e9m nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng &ldquo;B\u00f2 t\u00f3t&rdquo;. Anh b\u1ecb c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Nga l\u1ea5y b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. D\u1eabu cho v\u1eabn gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng David Silva kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00e0o l\u00ean tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n n\u00e0o cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 b\u1ecb thay ra s\u1edbm b\u1edfi l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng Iniesta trong hi\u1ec7p hai.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>David De Gea\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Gea\" title=\"De Gea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/162625-3.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>De Gea kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n v\u1eefng ch\u00e3i \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">De Gea l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean h\u01a1n c\u1ea3. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1edfi tranh, De Gea \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 l\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAnh kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u World Cup b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n. C\u00fa s\u00fat \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo b\u1ed7ng nhi\u00ean tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng khi De Gea b\u1eaft h\u1ee5t b\u00f3ng y h\u1ec7t nh\u1eefng ch\u00e0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nghi\u1ec7p d\u01b0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nX\u00e9t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1edf World Cup, De Gea c\u0169ng n\u1eb1m trong nh\u00f3m nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh k\u00e9m nh\u1ea5t. Trong s\u1ed1 7 c\u00fa s\u00fat ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t, De Gea ch\u1ec9 c\u1ee9u thua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi t\u1edbi 6 b\u00e0n thua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDe Gea c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u1ea3 penalty n\u00e0o \u1edf lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang v\u1edbi Nga. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 De Gea kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1edbm \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t De Gea xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u01a1n c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd gi\u00fap La Roja ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u h\u01a1n th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0110T&nbsp;T\u00e2y Ban Nha:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-bi-co-the-dan-dat-tay-ban-nha-sau-world-cup-2018-421-190427.html\">HLV B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft T\u00e2y Ban Nha sau World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ky-world-cup-cua-tay-ban-nha-khong-te-nhu-nguoi-ta-nghi-421-190397.html\">K\u1ef3 World Cup c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta ngh\u0129</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"925","checkdouble":"190435"},{"date":"17:14 05/07","title":"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/3/u23-viet-nam-nam-chung-bang-voi-nhat-ban-tai-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 khi c\u00f9ng \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D v\u00e0 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn khi hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m ph\u00e2n b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam v\u00e0 n\u1eef t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra. L\u00e1 th\u0103m \u0111\u01b0a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 U23 Pakistan v\u00e0 U23 Nepan - hai \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/U23-Viet-Nam-nam-chung-bang-voi-Nhat-Ban-tai-ASIAD-2018-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m chung b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nASIAD 2018 c\u00f3 24 \u0111\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 chia th\u00e0nh 6 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, 4 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 ba c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u0169ng s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb 14/8 \u0111\u1ebfn 1/9 t\u1ea1i Indonesia. C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 v\u00e0 th\u00eam 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i h\u01a1n. Ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 th\u1edf v\u1edbi HongKong, L\u00e0o v\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0i Loan.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018. \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng C v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a \u0110T n\u1eef Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Th\u00e1i Lan. \u0110\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i h\u01a1n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110T n\u1eef Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng C.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m chia b\u1ea3ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018:\u00a0</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>B\u1ea3ng A:</strong> Indonesia, H\u1ed3ng K\u00f4ng, L\u00e0o, \u0110\u00e0i B\u1eafc Trung Hoa</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>B\u1ea3ng B:</strong> Th\u00e1i Lan, Uzbekistan, Bangladesh, Qatar</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>B\u1ea3ng C:</strong> Iraq, Trung Qu\u1ed1c, Timor Leste, Syria</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>B\u1ea3ng D: </strong>Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Pakistan, Nepal</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>B\u1ea3ng E:</strong> H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Kyrgyzstan, Malaysia, Bahrain</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>B\u1ea3ng F:</strong> CHDCND Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean, Saudi Arabia, Iran, Myanmar</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m chia b\u1ea3ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u1eef t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018:\u00a0</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>B\u1ea3ng A:</strong> Indonesia, Maldives, \u0110\u00e0i B\u1eafc Trung Hoa, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>B\u1ea3ng B:</strong> Tajikistan, H\u1ed3ng K\u00f4ng, Trung Qu\u1ed1c, CHDCND Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>B\u1ea3ng C:</strong> Th\u00e1i Lan, Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u23-viet-nam-dung-toan-doi-thu-dang-gom-truoc-asiad-2018-168-190369.html\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee5ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/giup-slna-co-3-diem-phan-van-duc-nhan-duoc-loi-khen-co-canh-cua-doi-thu-168-189826.html\">Gi\u00fap SLNA c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/kem-mieng-u23-viet-nam-bong-da-thai-lan-gap-rut-chuan-bi-cho-asiad-168-188833.html\">K\u00e9m mi\u1ebfng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u00e1i Lan g\u1ea5p r\u00fat chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/goc-nhin-dt-han-quoc-can-su-gia-do-park-hang-seo-de-tao-dia-chan-o-world-cup-421-188831.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: \u0110T H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u1ea7n \u2018s\u1ef1 gi\u00e0 d\u01a1\u2019 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n World Cup</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/xuan-truong-tiec-vi-khong-duoc-di-xem-world-cup-2018-465-188289.html\">Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ebfc v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i xem World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/dtqg/hlv-park-hang-seo-mong-cac-cau-thu-u23-viet-nam-duoc-bao-ve-292-188283.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo: C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"924","checkdouble":"190436"},{"date":"16:57 05/07","title":"\u0110T Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup: T\u1ea1i sao kh\u00f4ng?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/29/dt-anh-vo-dich-world-cup-tai-sao-khong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u00ean b\u1ee5c nh\u1eadn danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn xa t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup hay EURO g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, \u0110T Anh ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 7 trong danh s\u00e1ch \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup theo \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u00e1i&nbsp;Paddy Power v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 c\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0103n 20.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 mang t\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y song HLV Gareth Southgate l\u1ea1i s\u1edf h\u1eefu trong tay m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0u tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea7y s\u1ef1 c\u00e1 t\u00ednh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Tunisisa v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 6-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edbm c\u00f3 v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. V\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i ch\u1eb3ng khi\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Southgate m\u1ea5t tinh th\u1ea7n m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i h\u1ecd c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Colombia \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u1eb7p \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111ang m\u1edf ra v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a x\u1ee9 s\u1edf S\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin \u0110T Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Colombia t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u1edf nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch T\u00e2y Ban Nha cay \u0111\u1eafng r\u1eddi cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i sau lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang 11m v\u1edbi \u0110T Nga, l\u00fac n\u00e0y, \u0110T Anh \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd s\u1ebd v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nguy hi\u1ec3m \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111ang kh\u00e1 s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 Colombia l\u1eabn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ebfp chung m\u00e2m v\u1edbi Tam s\u01b0 v\u1ec1 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lingard phat bieu ve DT Anh\" title=\"Lingard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/huyen-thoai-duc-du-doan-2-doi-vao-chung-ket-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Anh \u1edf nh\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5 t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. H\u1ecd ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi h\u00e0nh trang l\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1eadp th\u1ec3. &lsquo;Nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn binh Viking&rsquo; kh\u00f4ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng hay nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u01b0u t\u00fa trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh song b\u00f9 l\u1ea1i, s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n trong l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh con ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfn xa t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1edbi t\u1eeb l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e1ng tin c\u1eady. Cho t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y h\u1ecd m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi trong 3 tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. Tuy nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 B\u1eafc \u00c2u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00fang phong \u0111\u1ed9, \u0110T Anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1eafng \u1edf c\u1eb7p Nga/Croatia. Nh\u00ecn chung \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng &lsquo;chi\u1ebfu d\u01b0\u1edbi&rsquo; so v\u1edbi \u0110T Anh v\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111ang kh\u00e1 s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Southgate.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o ng\u00f4i sao<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Anh trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng thi\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean khi m\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng th\u00ec h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t. Vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao c\u0169ng l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Argentina hay B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. V\u00e0 khi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ecb phong t\u1ecfa, vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y s\u1edbm b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup T\u1ea1i sao kh\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup T\u1ea1i sao kh\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/neu-khong-vao-ban-ket-anh-se-co-mot-ky-world-cup-that-bai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>&nbsp;\u0110T Anh kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 n\u00e0o</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00fat kinh nghi\u1ec7m t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n v\u1ea5p ng\u00e3 trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, trong tay HLV Gareth Southgate, \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n n\u00e0o n\u1ed5i tr\u1ed9i, ngo\u00e0i Harry Kane. V\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng 47 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00fang ngh\u0129a d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng, \u00f4ng c\u1ea7n nh\u00e2n t\u00e0i ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao trong \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u1ebb, khao kh\u00e1t th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Colombia thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 v\u1ebb b\u1ea3n n\u0103ng v\u00e0 d\u01b0 th\u1eeba th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, kh\u00f4n ngoan v\u00e0 bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh bi\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1eddi. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cho th\u1ea5y Tam S\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t t\u00e2m l\u00fd, v\u00e0 l\u00e0 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 Anh d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 may m\u1eafn<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, may m\u1eafn lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi tuy\u1ec3n \u1edf, t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eeb th\u1ea7n may m\u1eafn.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>Ngay tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Tunisia, m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng s\u01a1 h\u1edf kh\u00f3 tin c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00fang ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Harry Kane tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi Panama v\u00e0 Colombia mang \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi h\u01a1n cho \u0110T Anh. Nh\u1edd c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y m\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00e1o g\u1ee1 nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>N\u00ean nh\u1edb, c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh t\u1eeb b\u1ec7 ph\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f3, Tam s\u01b0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ec7nh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady m\u1edbi th\u1ea5y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111ang r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup \u1edf l\u1ea7n t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00e3 52 n\u0103m k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi \u0110T Tam s\u01b0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ngay ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i qu\u00ea nh\u00e0, h\u1ecd m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn ch\u1ea1m tay v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap nh\u01b0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-anh-giong-voi-tay-ban-nha-nam-2010-421-190424.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/dt-anh-giong-voi-tay-ban-nha-nam-2010.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-anh-giong-voi-tay-ban-nha-nam-2010-421-190424.html\">\u0110T Anh gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u0103m 2010</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh \u1edf VCK World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, c\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 TBN Luis Garcia cho r\u1eb1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Gareth Southgate c\u00f3 n\u00e9t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cap-nhat-tinh-hinh-luc-luong-cua-dt-anh-truoc-tran-gap-thuy-dien-421-190432.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/cap-nhat-tinh-hinh-luc-luong-cua-dt-anh-truoc-tran-gap-thuy-dien.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cap-nhat-tinh-hinh-luc-luong-cua-dt-anh-truoc-tran-gap-thuy-dien-421-190432.html\">C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</span><br>\r\nAnh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd b\u00f3ng l\u0103n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tu-ket-world-cup-2018-hay-de-y-nguoi-anh-421-190417.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/tu-ket-world-cup-2018-hay-de-y-nguoi-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tu-ket-world-cup-2018-hay-de-y-nguoi-anh-421-190417.html\">T\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: H\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh</span><br>\r\nT\u1eeb m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1eb3ng ai quan t\u00e2m, \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u, sau khi \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"923","checkdouble":"190437"},{"date":"17:44 05/07","title":"S\u1ee3 PSG \u201ccu\u1ed7m\u201d Kante, Chelsea nh\u1eafm sao Lyon","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/15/chelsea-muon-mua-ndombele-thay-kante.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Ndombele thay Kante. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi khi bi\u1ebft tin PSG quy\u1ebft chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p h\u1ed3i h\u01b0\u01a1ng trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>PSG chi \u0111\u1eadm mua Kante</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nParis Saint-Germain xem N'Golo Kante c\u1ee7a Chelsea nh\u01b0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. D\u00f9 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 ph\u1ea3i chi ra c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean t\u1edbi 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ho\u1eb7c h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a Adrien Rabiot nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o, gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Antero Henrique c\u1ee7a PSG \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ec7nh ph\u1ea3i mang b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Kante v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 kh\u1edfi tranh. H\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng d\u00e0nh cho c\u1ef1u th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean Leicester City m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 220 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n, t\u0103ng 100 ngh\u00ecn b\u1ea3ng/ tu\u1ea7n so v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3i ng\u1ed9 \u0111ang nh\u1eadn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Ndombele thay Kante \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c PSG \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Ndombele thay Kante \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c PSG \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/15/chelsea-muon-mua-ndombele-thay-kante.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">PSG mu\u1ed1n chi \u0111\u1eadm mua Kante</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ngay c\u1ea3 khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, The Blues v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Kante v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00e3i ng\u1ed9 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>T\u00ednh ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n thay th\u1ebf</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Ndombele thay Kante n\u1ebfu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p b\u1ecb PSG h\u00fat h\u1ed3n. Ndombele t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 l\u00e0 Tanguy Ndombele Alvaro, sinh t\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p nh\u01b0ng g\u1ed1c Congo. Th\u00e1ng 12 t\u1edbi, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m n\u00e0y s\u1ebd tr\u00f2n 22 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ndombele trong mau ao Lyon\" title=\"Ndombele trong mau ao Lyon\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/Ndombele-trong-mau-ao-Lyon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Ndombele thay Kante</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u01a1i cho Lyon d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Amiens m\u00f9a 2017/18, Ndombele \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng. Anh chi\u1ebfm su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh Les Gones, ra s\u00e2n 50 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. S\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 song Ndombele c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 c\u00e0n l\u01b0\u1edbt t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ndombele, Lyon \u0111\u00e3 mua \u0111\u1ee9t anh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 8 tri\u1ec7u Euro. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, Chelsea v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng 9 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o U21 Ph\u00e1p nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Kante. Ngo\u00e0i ra, nh\u1eefng Tiemoue Bakayoko v\u00e0 Danny Drinkwater sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb thanh l\u00fd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Ndombele, Chelsea c\u00f2n nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Aleksandr Golovin c\u1ee7a CSKA Moscow. Ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a HLV Antonio Conte v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t v\u00e0 The Blues ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1t c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh ch\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-vuot-mat-con-moi-vi-real-madrid-172-190411.html\">Chelsea vu\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t con m\u1ed3i v\u00ec... Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-sap-co-tien-dao-tri-gia-53-trieu-bang-172-190389.html\">Chelsea s\u1eafp c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chi-ban-willian-cho-mu-voi-mot-dieu-kien-172-190352.html\">Chelsea ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Willian cho MU v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hang-hot-tuyen-nga-tiep-tuc-ban-tin-hieu-cho-chelsea-421-190313.html\">H\u00e0ng hot tuy\u1ec3n Nga ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1eafn t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u cho Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/juventus-san-sang-trao-doi-bom-tan-voi-chelsea-172-190279.html\">Juventus s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng trao \u0111\u1ed5i bom t\u1ea5n v\u1edbi Chelsea</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"922","checkdouble":"190438"},{"date":"17:30 05/07","title":"R\u00f4 b\u00e9o: \"Neymar c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng 2018\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/5/ro-beo-neymar-co-the-gianh-qua-bong-vang-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Neymar gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Brazil, R\u00f4 b\u00e9o.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u00f4 b\u00e9o tin Neymar c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh QBV 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Neymar ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o PSG. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a anh d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n 3 th\u00e1ng cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ro b\u00e9o tin Neymar gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng 2018 n\u1ebfu v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch WC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ro b\u00e9o tin Neymar gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng 2018 n\u1ebfu v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch WC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/ro-beo-neymar-co-the-gianh-qua-bong-vang-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ro b\u00e9o tin Neymar v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh QBV n\u1ebfu v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/cha-neymar-xac-nhan-cau-thu-nay-nghi-thi-dau-dai-ngay-184-181002.html\" target=\"_blank\">Neymar d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng</span> v\u00e0 PSG b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1edbm \u1edf Champions League, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf so v\u1edbi Ronaldo, ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch C1 2018 c\u00f9ng Real v\u00e0 Messi, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00f9ng Barca trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng 2018.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNeymar gi\u00e0nh Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Brazil, R\u00f4 b\u00e9o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cRonaldo v\u00e0 Messi \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi World Cup 2018, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Neymar th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. N\u1ebfu Neymar t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0a Brazil v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh b\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao, b\u1edfi v\u1eady c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Neymar v\u01b0\u1ee3t Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRonaldo c\u0169ng n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Neymar b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u, anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i c\u1ea7n b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ro b\u00e9o khen ng\u1ee3i HLV Tite</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo tin r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu HLV Tite \u0111\u01b0a Brazil v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 \u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u HLV c\u1ee7a n\u0103m.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Tite noi ve tran Brazil vs Mexico\" title=\"HLV Tite n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs Mexico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/hlv-tite-phat-bieu-ve-tran-brazil-vs-mexico.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ro b\u00e9o \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao HLV Tite</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Tite, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. Khi \u0111\u00f3 t\u00f4i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Tite \u1edf Corinthians. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi nhau 1 n\u0103m, th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc khi t\u00f4i v\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u h\u01a1n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cTite l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t HLV t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y nhanh nh\u1eady trong nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng HLV c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng xoay chuy\u1ec3n t\u00ecnh th\u1ebf r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. N\u1ebfu Brazil v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn danh hi\u1ec7u HLV c\u1ee7a n\u0103m\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"921","checkdouble":"190440"},{"date":"09:29 05/07","title":"T\u00e2n binh Liverpool l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u1ecdc t\u1ee9c Man Utd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/fabinho-khang-dinh-chua-tung-tien-gan-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fabinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Liverpool g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c c\u1ea3 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1edbi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/klopp-noi-gi-ve-qua-bom-tan-bat-ngo-fabinho-172-187241.html\" target=\"_blank\">qu\u1ea3 bom t\u1ea5n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd Fabinho 45-50 tri\u1ec7u Euro</span> m\u1edf m\u00e0n k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y, khi m\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n li\u00ean h\u1ec7 g\u00ec gi\u1eefa \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Champions League v\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Monaco.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u00e2n binh Fabinho c\u1ee7a Liverpool n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u00e2n binh Fabinho c\u1ee7a Liverpool n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/fabinho-khang-dinh-chua-tung-tien-gan-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>T\u00e2n binh Fabinho c\u1ee7a Liverpool n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00e1ng n\u00f3i h\u01a1n khi Fabinho t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Man Utd qua c\u00e1c phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, v\u1eady n\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1eddi chung kia n\u1eabng tay tr\u00ean trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00ednh ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cKh\u00f4ng, t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Man Utd li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f3.\u201d \u2013 Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c n\u00e0o ch\u1ecdc t\u1ee9c Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf th\u00e0nh Manchester c\u1ee7a Fabinho.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 nghe l\u1eddi ra l\u1eddi v\u00e0o v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c, n\u00f3 ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd s\u00e1ng s\u1ee7a v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t thi\u1ec7t m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 Monaco \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Man Utd nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp d\u00e0nh cho t\u00f4i th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Liverpool m\u1edbi nghi\u00eam t\u00fac v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i l\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ef1 v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Fabinho l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Liverpool trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 hai s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Anfield t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 1/7. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 t\u1eadn m\u1ed9t n\u0103m, nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Naby Keita t\u1eeb RB Leipzig v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/fabinho-sang-liverpool-them-mot-lan-cai-tat-vao-mu-172-187307.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/fabinho-sang-liverpool-them-mot-lan-cai-tat-vao-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/fabinho-sang-liverpool-them-mot-lan-cai-tat-vao-mu-172-187307.html\">Fabinho sang Liverpool: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n c\u00e1i t\u00e1t v\u00e0o MU</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tin n\u1ed5i, c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111a n\u0103ng Fabinho sang Liverpool qu\u00e1 nhanh, qu\u00e1 nguy hi\u1ec3m, nh\u01b0 phong c\u00e1ch t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ef1c l\u1eeda c\u1ee7a L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf m\u00f9a n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"920","checkdouble":"190403"},{"date":"09:15 05/07","title":"Neymar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ca ng\u1ee3i gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/willian-ca-ngoi-neymar-giua-nhung-chi-trich.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Willian ca ng\u1ee3i Neymar gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Chelsea tin ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i si\u00eau sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i hay h\u01a1n n\u1eefa t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Willian \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Neymar</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng kho\u1ea3ng n\u1eeda th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi World Cup 2018 khai m\u1ea1c, Neymar v\u1eabn th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3. 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 1/8 v\u1edbi Mexico, ch\u00ednh Neymar l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 khai th\u00f4ng th\u1ebf b\u1ebf t\u1eafc cho Brazil \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2. Cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh anh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1eadt ra, t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho Roberto Firmino \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 2-0 cho Selecao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willian ca ng\u1ee3i Neymar gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Willian ca ng\u1ee3i Neymar gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/willian-ca-ngoi-neymar-giua-nhung-chi-trich.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Willian ca ng\u1ee3i Neymar gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/neymar-duoc-khuyen-nen-tu-bo-nghiep-cau-thu-va-chon-nghe-dien-vien-421-190281.html\" target=\"_blank\">Neymar v\u1edbi h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0103n v\u1ea1 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e0</span> \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u1eeb d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn. V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n Willian, anh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Brazil \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Neymar trong \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ebf n\u00e0o\u201d, Willian ca ng\u1ee3i Neymar. \u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. K\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n, c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111i t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 may m\u1eafn.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNeymar l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec c\u00e1ch c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Courtois phat bieu ve DT Anh\" title=\"Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/25/bai-du-thi-an-tuong-world-cup-2018-bong-da-la-da-bong-da-bong-la-bong-da.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Willian d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Courtois</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nC\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a Brazil \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup l\u00e0 B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i v\u00e0o 1h ng\u00e0y 7/7 t\u1edbi. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c h\u1ed9i ng\u1ed9 gi\u1eefa Willian v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i Chelsea, Thibaut Courtois. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 29 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ca ng\u1ee3i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Courtois khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t gi\u1ecfi v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea1i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d, Willian n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Courtois v\u00e0 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 Courtois: Alisson, Ederson, Cassio. H\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Brazil tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/douglas-costa-binh-phuc-chan-thuong-421-190341.html\">Brazil nh\u1eadn tin vui tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/kompany-phat-bieu-truoc-tran-bi-vs-brazil-421-190392.html\">Kompany: B\u1ec9 s\u1ee3 g\u00ec c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao Brazil?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/brazil-thang-tien-tu-ket-chat-thep-quyen-lan-trong-nhung-vu-dieu-samba-421-190290.html\">Brazil th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft: Ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p quy\u1ec7n l\u1eabn trong nh\u1eefng v\u0169 \u0111i\u1ec7u Samba</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/vuot-qua-nhat-dt-bi-da-san-sang-truoc-brazil-421-190268.html\">V\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nh\u1eadt, \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/neymar-den-di-tiem-phong-cung-se-an-va-voi-bac-si-421-190267.html\">Neymar \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i ti\u00eam ph\u00f2ng c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0103n v\u1ea1 v\u1edbi b\u00e1c s\u0129!</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"919","checkdouble":"190404"},{"date":"09:59 05/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Juventus s\u1edbm m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 song s\u00e1t t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p Ronaldo - Higuain","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/nguoi-juventus-som-mo-ve-song-sat-tai-hop-ronaldo-higuain.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u00e2n binh Fabinho c\u1ee7a Liverpool kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n v\u1edbi s\u00e2n Old Trafford nh\u01b0 b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed3n th\u1ed5i trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9.</h2><h2>Fabinho kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/vi-sao-noi-fabinho-dang-gia-nhat-cua-chuyen-nhuong-mu-172-162081.html\" target=\"_blank\">Fabinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Man United \u01b0u ti\u00ean</span> chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 sau khi gi\u00fap Monaco gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ligue 1 v\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy v\u1eady, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c. V\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Fabinho \u00edt l\u00e2u sau khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fabinho kh\u00f4ng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi MU nh\u01b0 b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed3n th\u1ed5i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Fabinho kh\u00f4ng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi MU nh\u01b0 b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed3n th\u1ed5i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/6/13/Fabinho-khong-lien-he-voi-MU-nhu-bao-chi-don-thoi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Fabinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ee5t v\u1edbi MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 trong b\u00e0i tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n tr\u00ean t\u1edd FourFourTwo g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Fabinho \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c anh ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n Man United nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed3n th\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Man United. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ea5y nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edd b\u00e1o n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt th\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i bu\u1ed5i th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i t\u1ea1i Monaco. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Man United\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Fabinho kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n suy ngh\u0129 khi Liverpool \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng anh kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 nhi\u1ec1u khi Liverpool b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 anh h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cQuy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi t\u00f4i kh\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng bu\u1ed3n khi ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi Monaco. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t CLB mang l\u1ea1i cho t\u00f4i nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p. Nh\u01b0ng trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u0111\u00f4i khi b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNgay khi Liverpool b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c. Khi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed h\u00e0o h\u00f9ng nh\u01b0 Liverpool mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 b\u1ea1n th\u00ec b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3i h\u00e0nh l\u00fd v\u00e0 l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t vinh d\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 MU:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-0507-mu-va-chelsea-no-bom-tan-cung-luc-184-190395.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 05/07: MU v\u00e0 Chelsea n\u1ed5 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d c\u00f9ng l\u00fac</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-chi-ban-willian-cho-mu-voi-mot-dieu-kien-172-190352.html\">Chelsea ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Willian cho MU v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"918","checkdouble":"190405"},{"date":"10:08 05/07","title":"Ronaldo b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a Neymar","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/dan-anh-bao-ve-thoi-an-va-cua-neymar.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1eb3ng nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng khuy\u00ean nh\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e0n em, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ronaldo b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a Neymar v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed b\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng.\r\n</h2><h2>Neymar \u0103n v\u1ea1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang?<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Mexico v\u1eeba qua, si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn trong c\u1ea3 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, \u0111\u01b0a Selecao th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Neymar \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ef1c x\u1ea5u khi \u0103n v\u1ea1 th\u00f4 thi\u1ec3n d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea1m nh\u1eb9 v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch nh\u1eafm v\u00e0o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Neymar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean n\u00ean t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, b\u1edfi anh s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng gi\u1eadt gi\u1ea3i Oscar n\u1ebfu chuy\u1ec3n sang nghi\u1ec7p di\u1ec5n xu\u1ea5t. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, HLV \u0110T Ireland cho r\u1eb1ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/neymar-den-di-tiem-phong-cung-se-an-va-voi-bac-si-421-190267.html\" target=\"_blank\">Neymar \u0111i kh\u00e1m c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0103n v\u1ea1 v\u1edbi\u2026 b\u00e1c s\u0129</span>.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch n\u00e0y, \u201cNg\u01b0\u1eddi ngo\u00e0i h\u00e0nh tinh\u201d Ronaldo de Lima l\u1ea1i ngh\u0129 kh\u00e1c. Anh cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cC\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1ch xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 di\u1ec5n gi\u1ea3i n\u00f3. \u00dd ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda Neymar, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch n\u00e0o h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a Neymar tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ronaldo b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a Neymar tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Ronaldo-bao-ve-thoi-an-va-cua-Neymar-truoc-nhung-chi-trich-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 Ronaldo b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a Neymar</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNeymar l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u00f4ng minh \u1edf nh\u1eefng pha di chuy\u1ec3n, v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch c\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n kh\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng pha va ch\u1ea1m. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 c\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cKhi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, t\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu. Ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch khi \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eb3ng khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i b\u1eadn t\u00e2m. Nh\u1eefng ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh v\u00e0 b\u00e1o ch\u00ed ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n l\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ea7y th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ph\u00e1t s\u00f3ng, v\u00e0 h\u1ecd lu\u00f4n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee9 v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y Jose Mourinho c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng pha \u0103n v\u1ea1 trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. J<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/sau-neymar-gio-lai-co-dien-vien-henderson-421-190346.html\" target=\"_blank\">ordan Henderson c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0103n v\u1ea1 th\u00f4 thi\u1ec3n</span>, v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 to l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 Harry Maguire c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n th\u1eed s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh l\u00e0m \u201cth\u1ee3 l\u1eb7n.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 v\u1eady, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Ronaldo b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a Neymar kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf. Neymar m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i. \u1ede k\u1ef3 World Cup 2014 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, anh c\u0169ng b\u1ecb h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Colombia ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o, v\u00e0 su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7 v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Clip C\u0110V Mexico di\u1ec5n l\u1ea1i th\u00f3i \u0103n v\u1ea1 c\u1ee7a Neymar<br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/3/mexico.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/neymar-duoc-khuyen-nen-tu-bo-nghiep-cau-thu-va-chon-nghe-dien-vien-421-190281.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/neymar-duoc-khuyen-nen-tu-bo-nghiep-cau-thu-va-chon-nghe-dien-vien.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/neymar-duoc-khuyen-nen-tu-bo-nghiep-cau-thu-va-chon-nghe-dien-vien-421-190281.html\">Neymar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u00ean n\u00ean t\u1eeb b\u1ecf nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn ngh\u1ec1 di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00e1ng x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5 trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Mexico 2-0, ng\u00f4i sao Brazil \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch tr\u00ean to\u00e0n th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u00fd ki\u1ebfn v\u1ec1 h\u00ecnh...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-che-duoc-ronaldo-va-messi-ru-ve-nuoc-neymar-mim-cuoi-noi-khong-421-190277.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/anh-che-duoc-ronaldo-va-messi-ru-ve-nuoc-neymar-mim-cuoi-noi-khong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/anh-che-duoc-ronaldo-va-messi-ru-ve-nuoc-neymar-mim-cuoi-noi-khong-421-190277.html\">\u1ea2nh ch\u1ebf: \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi r\u1ee7 v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc, Neymar m\u1ec9m c\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng t\u01b0\u1edfng World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c x\u1ea3y ra nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd, nh\u01b0ng Brazil v\u1eabn \u1edf l\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga chinh chi\u1ebfn. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh Neymar t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Ronaldo v\u00e0...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"917","checkdouble":"190406"},{"date":"09:40 05/07","title":"Matuidi tin Mbappe s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1eafn h\u1ea1 Uruguay \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/matuidi-khang-dinh-mbappe-se-toa-sang-hon-nua.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Blaise Matuidi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh sao tr\u1ebb Kylian Mbappe s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng d\u00f9 Uruguay c\u00f3 b\u00e0y binh b\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</h2><h2>Mbappe r\u1ef1c s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a PSG \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 1/8 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> gi\u1eefa Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Argentina. Mbappe ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfm v\u1ec1 cho Les Bleus 1 qu\u1ea3 penalty trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap \u0111\u00f3, Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 2 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i d\u01b0\u1edbi 20 l\u1eadp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap \u1edf m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i World Cup sau \u201cVua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1\u201d Pele.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 kinh ho\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb 19 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f4 v\u00e0n kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Jorge Sampaoli. V\u00e0 Uruguay ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Uruguay kh\u00f3 ng\u0103n ch\u1eb7n Mbappe\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mbappe s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng d\u00f9 Uruguay b\u00e0y binh b\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn ra sao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mbappe s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng d\u00f9 Uruguay b\u00e0y binh b\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn ra sao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/matuidi-khang-dinh-mbappe-se-toa-sang-hon-nua.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Matuidi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Mbappe s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng d\u00f9 Uruguay b\u00e0y binh b\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn ra sao</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 Matuidi m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng Mbappe ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa, b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p Uruguay s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f3a ch\u1eb7t anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cTheo d\u00f5i Mbappe ng\u00e0y qua ng\u00e0y tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp, t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu nh\u00f3c n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec9nh d\u00f9 kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng \u00edt \u1ecfi \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cK\u00e8m c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 di chuy\u1ec3n gi\u1eefa nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng nh\u1ecf nh\u1ea5t. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y thay \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t nhanh. V\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t th\u00fa v\u1ecb \u1edf kho\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cK\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 Uruguay l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f3 nh\u1eb1n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cho \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng n\u00e0o th\u00ec Mbappe c\u0169ng s\u1ebd t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Mbappe:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/varane-mbappe-mang-hinh-bong-cua-ro-beo-469-190173.html\">Varane: Mbappe mang h\u00ecnh b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Ro b\u00e9o</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/pogba-tang-boc-mbappe-len-may-sau-tran-dai-thang-argentina-469-190086.html\">Pogba th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng b\u1eb1ng Mbappe</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"916","checkdouble":"190408"}]}